name: Tube bead resin necklace, striped rainbow multicolor
description: Comfortable and leightweight design necklace made from handmade resin beads. 25 tubular resin beads build this extraordinary necklace. Each bead was handmade of resin, cast in stripes and different bright colors, like red, orange, pastel green, pastel blue, yellow and dark red. Unique piece.The surface of the beads is matte and there are a few tiny bubbles to be found on the edges. The beads are mounted on a black leather cord (0,039 in / 1 mm) and moveable on the cord.Ends of cord are knotted, so the beads will not get lost.The necklace is changeable in length and closed by a knot in the neck. Shown in photo is a length of 27,55 in / 70 cm. Biggest bead has a diameter of 0,98 - 1,18 in / 2,5 - 3 cm.Weight: 2,11 oz / 60 g. From the "flirting with disorder"-necklace series. The arrangement is shifting and changing with each movement, the beads are falling out of place. Extraordinay and unique look!Interested in handmade jewelry and accessoires? More on www.ednamo.com

description: This unique hand made wood ring is for daily use, is washable, waterproof and a lot more resistant than many drilled out wooden rings. Its hard-wearing nature makes it the perfect gift for him or her. It could also be used as a rustic wedding ring, or alternative engagement ring,  or just to celebrate your friendship.This unisex ring is made  from several layers of veneer, SaRaiFo - mahagoni wood lines the inside, with Alpi Makassar wood at the surface, which provides toughness and a unique look.Please notice, that every order is a custom order. It is the nature of the material that every ring will have its own unique apperance.Also important to know is, that all venners from "Alpi" and "SaRaiFo" (Save the Rainforest)  are replica from real wood to save the important habitats of the rainforest.Thank you for visiting my shop.
